  "dragonsurvival.advancement.wing_kirin/be_wing_kirin": "九天来客",
  "dragonsurvival.advancement.wing_kirin/be_wing_kirin.desc": "历经数重考验，化为一条翼麒麟。",
  "dragonsurvival.advancement.wing_kirin/be_wing_kirin.message": "§b青云§r与§6时光不匆§r敬献。",
