  "dragonsurvival.advancement.wing_kirin/great_zhengqi": "浩然正气",
  "dragonsurvival.advancement.wing_kirin/great_zhengqi.desc": "从「龙之信标」获得「浩然正气」效果，让你在离开主世界时不必时刻提心吊胆。",
  "dragonsurvival.advancement.wing_kirin/weather_clear": "云销雨霁",
