  "dragonsurvival.advancement.wing_kirin/the_wine_from_empyrean": "玉瓶珍馐",
  "dragonsurvival.advancement.wing_kirin/the_wine_from_empyrean.desc": "皓月当空时在云端之上用空玻璃瓶收集天地日月的精华，方可得此一瓶仙露。",
  "dragonsurvival.advancement.wing_kirin/heaven_dish": "天上佳肴",
  "dragonsurvival.advancement.wing_kirin/heaven_dish.desc": "食下这一份佳肴，顿觉法力大增，施放自如！",
  "dragonsurvival.advancement.wing_kirin/ding_shen_shu": "定！",
  "dragonsurvival.advancement.wing_kirin/ding_shen_shu.desc": "用「定身术」给对手点上“死穴”，使其动弹不得，“我为刀俎，他为鱼肉”。",
  "dragonsurvival.advancement.wing_kirin/falling_arrow_like_rainstorm": "暴雨梨花针",
  "dragonsurvival.advancement.wing_kirin/falling_arrow_like_rainstorm.desc": "朝天上打上一发「穿云箭」，让敌卒体会下什么叫“万箭穿心”。",
  "dragonsurvival.advancement.wing_kirin/overoveroverkill": "从天而降",
  "dragonsurvival.advancement.wing_kirin/overoveroverkill.desc": "使用重锤一击造成250颗心的伤害，将“势大力沉”体现得淋漓尽致。",
  "dragonsurvival.advancement.wing_kirin/fly_higher": "高处不胜寒",
  "dragonsurvival.advancement.wing_kirin/fly_higher.desc": "飞至999格的碧空之上，好生领悟苏轼的“我自乘风归去”。",
  "dragonsurvival.advancement.wing_kirin/delay_death": "回光返照",
  "dragonsurvival.advancement.wing_kirin/delay_death.desc": "触发「回光返照」后天被动，“阎王要你三更死，它能留你到五更。”",
  "dragonsurvival.advancement.wing_kirin/be_old": "统御青天",
  "dragonsurvival.advancement.wing_kirin/be_old.desc": "身为翼麒麟成长至108成长等级。",
