  "dragonsurvival.advancement.wing_kirin/invincible_benevolence":"仁者无敌",
  "dragonsurvival.advancement.wing_kirin/invincible_benevolence.desc":"单次使至少3名以上的盟友受惠之于你的「仁者无敌」，用醒目的效果时长来“诠释”古人的智慧。",
